Making this page

Setting up everything on Git and RStudio was easy since I had used them previously. I used the guide on this page to clone the GitHub repository for homework 1 via RStudio. For using Markdown, this GitHub guide was helpful. At first I couldn’t figure out how to preview my Markdown file, but then I followed the instructions on this page to install the R Markdown package, which opened up the “Preview HTML” option in RStudio.
